            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-3">
                <a href="/" class="w-full sm:w-auto text-center bg-brand hover:bg-brand-light text-white font-bold text-[14px] px-6 py-3 rounded-full transition">
                    Retour à l'accueil
                </a>
                <a href="javascript:history.back()" class="w-full sm:w-auto text-center bg-surface hover:bg-line text-ink-soft font-semibold text-[14px] px-6 py-3 rounded-full transition">
